{"pid":"8bd26529b1a0bfe8b2b0324d455144a64c385acb","tid":241660,"uid":12518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T23:29:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b02ea4c109bcca3db1674c8d7ec97db58c371784","tid":241660,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T00:05:01.000Z","msg":"紅登不願面對<br />\n派五毛來搞事"},{"pid":"41e3a6f37713ae0dfe0b466b14991f371f5c7e65","tid":241660,"uid":60720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T00:16:30.000Z","msg":"樓主，魔戰盃az盃幾時出結果"},{"pid":"08df67d6d5c892bc17da320e1ecef4b2bf663f27","tid":241660,"uid":30453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T07:10:53.000Z","msg":"好係時候收手<br />\n<br />\n無論你覺得小學雞lf2負評點都好<br />\n我實畀人話咩小事放上網之類<br />\n所以呢啲我認咗先唔洗煩<br />\n順便認埋柒咗先廢事全部都淨係回咩柒咗嬲<br />\n<br />\n而點解我要做小學雞同佢地一齊死<br />\n原因就係就係個個都硬食佢地先敢繼續玩<br />\n網上lf2但唯一玩法係咁<br />\n唔係就等佢地繼續玩人晒人地時間<br />\n唔係個個都係廢青好得閒<br />\n<br />\n我的確係標題黨<br />\n但呢單小學雞野的確有關高登同連登<br />\n而連登apps台啲人的確好熱心幫人<br />\n<br />\n唔鐘意嘅歡迎負評屌鳩我<br />\n個個人意見都唔同<br />\n我嘅角色只係扮嬲嬲豬企出嗰個<br />\n之後重有野講"},{"pid":"3efb0641f12df31b9cd028871c9868ce4bed5baa","tid":241660,"uid":30453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T07:12:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/15/151119_d4a3876cbb7eb6d4b332ff5265a64b6b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F15%2F151119_d4a3876cbb7eb6d4b332ff5265a64b6b.jpg&h=bff852d0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/15/151119_9ab5205e1de4bb7509dc3254cf01e7e3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F15%2F151119_9ab5205e1de4bb7509dc3254cf01e7e3.jpg&h=33c1c94a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e4cee31309e74a6f2ba01d5402e8be035a6c4c63","tid":241660,"uid":30453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T07:27:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/15/151254_f2fb90693378906c992850bd4e03deda.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F15%2F151254_f2fb90693378906c992850bd4e03deda.jpg&h=e43d9c3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我係連登開post<br />\n但高登班小學雞mon post玩人<br />\n重要迫人上返高登<br />\n惡過共產黨<br />\n呢度貼題<br />\n如果咁都無問題<br />\n咁大家過連登做咩"},{"pid":"a4c507ba74dc45f7c29cd505cef62d3bbf54d34d","tid":241660,"uid":87134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T07:28:31.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪上連登上到痴咗線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bacf64efc5f5b968ce258f1b1bb87d1bb83af3f9","tid":241660,"uid":30453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T07:31:11.000Z","msg":"我明明係連登開post<br />\n但就成班高登mon post mk<br />\n入嚟玩野<br />\nline group我開嘅又唔係入佢地<br />\n你可以話玩人係高登連登風氣<br />\n我先唔講飛過壇高登去連登呢個問題<br />\n平時假膠玩人post都係引人入玩野<br />\n但佢地係主動搞人<br />\n平時主動攻擊玩嘅都係啲公開派膠/公開言論有問題嘅人<br />\n又咩起底fb攻擊之類<br />\n啲5p呀蝗字撚入連登post都畀人屌啦<br />\n定係本是同根生<br />\n高登連登一家親"}]}